text: Almetovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bik-Karmalinsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 24 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Davlekanovo, 4 km from Bik-Karmaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Almetovo
